name: Jordan 8.0 (White/Grey)
description:
Jordan 8.0 Men's Basketball Shoes

The Jordan 8.0 has given a makeover to the legendary Retro VIII with a lower, sleeker construction and a few new technical updates to make this style faster and more efficient on the court. The one major detail that remains are the criss-cross straps across the midfoot that sets the 8 apart in the Jordan series. On the upper, you have a combination of synthetics and suede along with Flywire that has been introduced to reduce the bulkiness of the previous model. The outsole has been updated with lighter, more comfortable technology along with a slightly different paint splatter design at the midsole. 
• Get your Jordan 8.0 at The Last Pair with brand new technology and feature updates that make this Jordan game shoe a must-have.
• Flywire added to the upper
• Lower, sleeker construction

name: Adidas Mutombo Shoe (White/Black)
description:
Adidas Mutombo Shoe

First released in 1993 for 4-time NBA defensive player of the year Dikembe Mutombo, this adidas Originals basketball shoe is being re-released into the game. Iconic 90's styling and African inspired details honor Mutombo's journey from the Congo to the court.
Original hi top design
Iconic shield logo features Mutombo's number 55
Re-released cloth pattern inspired by Mutombo's African heritage

name: Reebok Shaq Attaq (Black/Azure)
description:
Men's Reebok Shaq Attaq Basketball Shoes
The Reebok Shaq signature line is back on the market with another banger. Meet the Men's Reebok Shaq Attaq Basketball Shoes, boasting incredible swag that matches the aura of the legend's larger-than-life personality.
Made with a leather upper with synthetic overlays, these hoops kicks deliver a superior fit and feel, getting your feet ventilation and support where they need it most. Ball in confidence thanks to a thick rubber sole and high-top design that work in unison to ensure you're secure and stable, on and off the court.
From the hardwood to the streets, spark sneaker envy in the most seasoned of sneakerheads with the Shaq Attaq's OG colorways. Two decades separate the original release and this re-issue, and there's no doubt these will fly off the shelves. Cop a pair, drip '90s swag, ball, repeat.
FEATURES:
•	UPPER: Leather
•	OUTSOLE: Rubber
•	IMPORTED

name: Jordan 6-17-23 (White/Red/Black)
description:
Jordan 6-17-23 Men's Basketball Shoe
A hybrid mix of the Jordan Retro 6, 17 and 23, this shoe features a combo upper with nubuck and smooth leather features with heel tab for easy on pull. The midsole is a good mixture of the two shoes while the outsole uses strategically placed ice clear rubber pieces in a nice mixture of the three outsoles.
•	A hybrid mix of the Jordan Retro 6, 17 and 23.

name: Retro Jordan V (White/Black/Red)
description:
Air Jordan Retro 5 Basketball Shoes
Inspired by Michael Jordan's continued flight status and a WWII fighter plane the Air Jordan 5 was another custom Tinker Hatfield tinkered to perfection. With another scoring title under his belt and a 69 point outbreak against the Cavaliers, Jordan needed a shoe that would live up to his elevated game. 
1990 proved to be a good year, Michael's aerial attack inspired the WWII Spitfire flames on the 5s. This shoe introduced a padded tongue displaying a continuance of the iconic jumpman logo, and a first for clear rubber outsoles. Additionally, a plastic lace-lock, full-grain leather and Durabuk and side vents converge to form a fighter like shoe ready for takeoff. 
FEATURES:
•	UPPER: Full-grain leather and Durabuk
•	OUTSOLE: Rubber
•	IMPORTED

name: Jordan Spizike (Fire Red)
description:
Men's Jordan Spizike Basketball Shoes
Drawing on the iconic styles that have helped shape footwear for years, the Jordan Spizike Men's Basketball Shoe is a hybrid of epic proportions. Taking the best of the Jordan III, IV, V and VI and peppering in some stylistic input from director Spike Lee, the Spizike is a sleek tribute to footwear innovation and artistic creativity. With Air-Sole units in the heel and forefoot to absorb impact, this sneaker is as comfortable on the court as it in the street. 
FEATURES:
•	UPPER: Leather and synthetic upper with mesh side panels
•	MIDSOLE: Polyurethane midsole with Air-Sole units in the heel and forefoot 
•	OUTSOLE: Rubber

name: Retro Jordan X (Stealth)
description:
Men's Jordan Retro 10 Basketball Shoes
The Jordan Retro 10 (X) Men's Shoes might remind you of the Air Jordan X. With leather upper and some suede for durability, the retro Jordan's are fairly simple and straightforward. A Jumpman logo on the back and outsole adds style, and you can't forget the outsole that lists Jordan's accomplishments. 
•	Shop for Air Jordan Retro 10 (X) Men's Shoes from The Final Pair. Features leather upper with some suede, Jumpman logos and outsole with Jordan's accomplishments. 
•	Reminiscent styling of the Air Jordan X. 
•	An outsole that features all of Jordan's major accomplishments
